<p>168. In a letter dated 3 October 2006, the Permanent Mission for the Republic of China replied
to the communication of 20 July 2006, concerning<b> Zheng Enchong</b> and <b>Jiang Meili. </b>The
Government noted that it had carefully investigated the matters referred to in the aforementioned
